      "oddsUpdateTime": "0001-01-01T01:00:00.000Z",
      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. IN TIMING went forward and gave a great sight before finishing third last time out over 1673m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic). Finds a suitable race and can take this out. 6. SHE'S CHLOE is yet to break through in three runs. Finished fifth at her last appearance over 1673m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic) on March 21. Well placed on this occasion and gets her chance to break the ice. 7. CLOCKLIKE was safely held last start on debut over 1106m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic). Should appreciate the longer journey now. Will strip fitter and can do much better. 4. SLICEAWAY is close to breaking through, last start finishing just 0.3 lengths away in second over 1609m at this track (Turf). Nicely placed to take this out.\",\"runners\":[8,6,7,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
